          <p class='first-para'>
            Will the hon. Gentleman remind me in reply to whom that answer was given? Is
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_203wh' title='Col. 203WH &mdash; HC Deb 12 July 2000 vol 353 c203WH' name='column_203wh' href='#column_203wh' rel='bookmark'>203WH</a>
            he suggesting that there was collusion between a member of another party over that question in the House of Lords?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
