          <p class='first-para'>
            Order. I am sure that the Under-Secretary would not wish to
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_221wh' title='Col. 221WH &mdash; HC Deb 12 July 2000 vol 353 c221WH' name='column_221wh' href='#column_221wh' rel='bookmark'>221WH</a>
            mislead the Chamber. The hon. Member for Altrincham and Sale, West (Mr. Brady) spoke for 52, not 45, minutes.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0353P0-04695'>
